{"tid":2311203,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"德國人權報告罕有直接抨擊中國　指新疆和香港人權狀況惡化","createTime":"2020-12-04T01:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T01:31:28.000Z","uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e440b5e5826249fc68ae1e6a55649d5b97f26034","tid":2311203,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:19:05.000Z","msg":"德國人權報告罕有直接抨擊中國 指新疆和香港人權狀況惡化<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20201204/mobile/bkn-20201204011840799-1204_00992_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fintnews%2F20201204%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20201204011840799-1204_00992_001.html&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=588843b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20201204/mobile/bkn-20201204011840799-1204_00992_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7bd538a2562621d1c02c61b0d82fdb27cac443c7","tid":2311203,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:19:35.000Z","msg":"德國政府日前在兩年一度的人權政策報告中，罕有地以直接口吻抨擊中國的人權問題，並指出新疆和香港人權狀況惡化。<br />\n德國外交部周三（2日）公布該份報告，關於中國的部分一開頭即指出，延續2012年以來的惡化趨勢，公民社會的空間愈來愈小，公民權、言論和新聞自由、學術、信仰自由等個人權利也受到限制，部分維權律師還被判刑入獄多年。<br />\n報告又指，新疆和西藏的人權狀況尤其惡劣，由於迫害、監視和大規模拘禁導致新疆人權持續惡化，並出現強制勞動和強制性的生育控制。德國亦認為，中國今年雖然通過民法典，但司法機關仍受控於黨，沒有確保法治國家的基本原則；中國並爭取成為聯合國人權理事會的成員，在國際上宣傳發展權以及國家安全高於個人權利的論述。<br />\n報告亦指，香港人權在過去兩年也有惡化趨勢，港區國安法打擊香港的公民社會、反對派人士和獨立媒體，導致確保香港高度自治的「一國兩制」原則被架空。<br />\n德國國會議員、人權委員會主席延森（Gyde Jensen）指出，這份人權報告顯示，德國政府終於意識到中國人權問題的嚴重性，但她也批評德政府缺乏實際作為，與中國實際互動時不管人權問題。"},{"pid":"ed943acce14d6a8fcef77bdbd82455fa492e9e56","tid":2311203,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:22:11.000Z","msg":"真係好小見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />德國肥婆為左賣車，不嬲都隻眼開隻眼閉"},{"pid":"5f59a34b0444bc5b509fb98477c400bd2950967a","tid":2311203,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:26:04.000Z","msg":"仲係惡化， 都幾mild<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0f29de468d635681f6b5a12dd2a4929416d1d2","tid":2311203,"uid":56819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed943acce14d6a8fcef77bdbd82455fa492e9e56","tid":2311203,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:22:11.000Z","msg":"真係好小見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />德國肥婆為左賣車，不嬲都隻眼開隻眼閉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:28:15.000Z","msg":"咪又係得把口,可以做得咩?"},{"pid":"8cdc2d62344d91db949362418591fddcca1b9e09","tid":2311203,"uid":18477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:31:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>白粉唔好貼link</strong></span></span>"}]}